summary: AN ORDINANCE approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 6312 for the improvement of 14th Avenue Southwest from approximately 30 feet south of Southwest Donovan Street to approximately 160 feet north thereof; and from Southwest Sullivan Street to approximately 100 feet north of Southwest Elmgrove Street and certain other streets, alleys and an easement by constructing sanitary sewers and otherwise improving the same.
